ces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f6bccd8a913bf904bc08d17e4dd41dcc1b4ffe7","tid":1946491,"uid":25659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T16:51:30.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n負到痴線<br />\n一方面覺得有機會休息下<br />\n但同時愈留係屋企愈覺得浪費時間<br />\n禁電話禁到無野好禁<br />\n頸又痛頭又痛<br />\n又會諗好多自己未來 覺得好徬徨<br />\n<br />\n雖然本身未有疫情都簡唔中會咁諗<br />\n但起碼會出下街無咁多時間亂諗"},{"pid":"7a45d8edd6f43dc924e156ab546caa7519736e33","tid":1946491,"uid":96135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T17:29:56.000Z","msg":"因為感情問題 <br />\n個人開咗負面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開始有失眠問題。<br />\n陣間5點起身返工 <br />\n但宜家都未訓到<br />\n嘗過過飲酒 但原來都係無用"},{"pid":"60f27c7d3e70a1e6ded252e606a2b6234ead7aa8","tid":1946491,"uid":188172,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T17:35:59.000Z","msg":"本身自己都係好負面既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依排又唔洗返工，<br />\n同男朋友見少左，<br />\n佢本身又唔係成日傾電話facetime既人，<br />\n搞到成日亂諗嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c77f9ca33add02730d2bbb543ccc384f118579","tid":1946491,"uid":207336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T17:48:00.000Z","msg":"分左手 想出去透透氣但因為有肺炎<br />\n日日睇到新聞好壓抑<br />\n睇到日日有人死，感覺好差，覺得生命好脆弱<br />\n諗返送中831，好重無力感"},{"pid":"f15eb30ce81d7b3791a40557b7f5657ecd49ba51","tid":1946491,"uid":92334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T18:00:16.000Z","msg":"成日都好頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cbfb40903e6cc8964047f57837251fa8449cad0","tid":1946491,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbec0a36d4fc4001a3eec4c8de621e46675b695f","tid":1946491,"uid":255210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T16:02:22.000Z","msg":"唔知因為疫情關係少左出街 <br />\n學又唔洗返 Frd都少見左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人好似好易就會亂諗嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n情緒唔係好穩定<br />\n我地幾時先打完呢場仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T08:41:19.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，到我們的網站             <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3filkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=5c768d9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"6061f392115c33f6265d971d66ebdf121be1011b","tid":1946491,"uid":205043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T08:46:06.000Z","msg":"屋企有既game已經俾我打爆晒<br />\n本身有跑開步但而家都已經唔敢去公園<br />\n本身對動漫又唔係好大興趣<br />\n有賭開波，但係呢期又冇波踢唯有局住賭畜生<br />\n<br />\n簡單d講就係悶到抽筋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日對住政事又真係好容易搞到唔開心<br />\n<br />\n共勉之啦"},{"pid":"74fa1fe4660e9bc8ba9a9ee4ce2c460a74835856","tid":1946491,"uid":296890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d6bb983cd4bd7bcf8115f3f33305ca7ba9f2708","tid":1946491,"uid":84172,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T16:28:42.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n呢個月成日無啦啦都喊得岀 返工又喊 搭車又喊<br />\n懷疑自己有情緒問題<br />\n唔知點算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T18:35:30.000Z","msg":"Me too<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}